---
// Meta banner for transparency communication (US-001)
---

<section data-test="meta-banner" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-purple-50 dark:from-blue-900/20 dark:to-purple-900/20 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-3">
    <div class="text-center text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-1.5 text-blue-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
        </svg>
        <strong>Transparency Notice:</strong>
      </span>
      This site was generated from a ~100-line product description using the RootSpec methodology.
      View the original
      <a
        href="https://github.com/rootspec/demos/blob/main/greenfield/SEED.md"
        data-test="spec-link"
        class="underline hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        SEED.md file
      </a>
      and the
      <a
        href="https://github.com/rootspec/demos/tree/main/greenfield/rootspec"
        class="underline hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        generated specification
      </a>
      on GitHub.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>